{"word":"H1576 - גְּמוּל - gᵉmûwl - ghem-ool' - As hast served","slug":"H1576","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גְּמוּל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>gᵉmûwl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ghem-ool'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>As hast served"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05DE;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05DC; - <a href='S:g'>g</a><sup>e</sup>mu&#x0302;l</b> - <i>ghem-ool'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H1580\">H1580</a>; <i>treatment</i>, that is, an <i>act</i> (of good or ill); by implication <i>service</i> or <i>requital: - </i>+ as hast served, benefit, desert, deserving, that which he hath given, recompence, reward."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1577\">H1577</a>, <a href=\"#/H1578\">H1578</a>, <a href=\"#/H1580\">H1580</a>, <a href=\"#/H1581\">H1581</a>, <a href=\"#/H1582\">H1582</a>, <a href=\"#/H1583\">H1583</a>, <a href=\"#/H8408\">H8408</a>"}]}